604
00:32:55,438 --> 00:32:58,806
why don't you and I go up
to the bedroom and--

605
00:32:58,807 --> 00:32:59,994
Make the cake.

606
00:33:00,914 --> 00:33:02,808
Well, you really are hungry.

607
00:33:03,700 --> 00:33:06,322
