608
00:33:10,269 --> 00:33:12,772
He wants you to make
a pineapple upside-down cake--

609
00:33:12,773 --> 00:33:15,350
The woman who ordered in
Chinese for Christmas?

610
00:33:15,351 --> 00:33:19,145
Yes, we've already covered that.
Now what am I gonna do?

611
00:33:19,146 --> 00:33:20,161
If I can't make this,

612
00:33:20,162 --> 00:33:22,169
