00:33:45,526 --> 00:33:48,809
First, I'm gonna preheat
my oven to 300.

621
00:33:49,746 --> 00:33:52,219
Then we're gonna start
with the caramel topping.

622
00:33:52,985 --> 00:33:55,367
And then we're gonna start
with the caramel topping...

623
00:33:56,830 --> 00:33:58,272
for which I will need...

624
