682
00:37:35,996 --> 00:37:38,727
out of my way!
Hot cake!

683
00:37:40,423 --> 00:37:42,479
Okay, but while we are waiting,

684
00:37:42,480 --> 00:37:44,889
there's just one thing
I have to say.

685
00:37:44,890 --> 00:37:49,214
Hey. This is not about a cake.
This is about trust.

686
00:37:49,215 --> 00:37:52,290
It is a sad day when a husband
forces a wife to bake for him

687
00:37:52,291 --> 00:37:54,271
just to prove she's not a liar.

688
00:37:54,514 --> 00:37:56,436
Do you have any idea
how offensive that is?

689
00:37:56,437 --> 00:37:57,566
Cake's ready.

690
00:38:02,318 --> 00:38:08,003
Ahh. There. One perfect
pineapple upside down cake.

691
00:38:09,450 --> 00:38:11,929
If only trust were so easy to make.

692
00:38:38,638 --> 00:38:40,179
You look surprised.

693
00:38:42,686 --> 00:38:43,765
I am.

694
00:38:45,027 --> 00:38:46,215
After the way I talked to you,

695
00:38:46,216 --> 00:38:49,426
