730
00:40:46,356 --> 00:40:47,659
Stop it. I'm gonna be late.

731
00:40:47,660 --> 00:40:50,199
Late for what?
Weekend getaway with Bree?

732
00:40:50,954 --> 00:40:52,689
Damn it, Gaby.
I forbade you to see her.

733
00:40:52,690 --> 00:40:54,877
Well, that was your first mistake.
What did you expect?

734
00:40:54,878 --> 00:40:57,186
I expected you to choose me!

735
00:41:00,412 --> 00:41:01,846
You know, ever since
we moved to this street,

736
00:41:01,847 --> 00:41:04,807
and--and you got so tight
with those women,

737
00:41:06,113 --> 00:41:07,834
I always feel like you put them first.

738
00:41:07,835 --> 00:41:09,418
You know that's not true.

739
00:41:10,800 --> 00:41:11,826
Prove it.

740
00:41:13,268 --> 00:41:14,341
Choose.

741
00:41:15,154 --> 00:41:17,617
Who do you want in your life--
me or Bree?

742
00:41:18,443 --> 00:41:19,647
