743
00:41:20,041 --> 00:41:21,463
I am doing it, Gaby.

744
00:41:25,701 --> 00:41:26,728
Choose.

745
00:41:28,797 --> 00:41:31,767
Yes, the residents of Wisteria Lane

746
00:41:31,768 --> 00:41:34,386
are nothing if not loyal,

747
00:41:35,123 --> 00:41:37,498
but there are times
when that loyalty

748
00:41:37,499 --> 00:41:39,464
is put to the test...

749
00:41:41,084 --> 00:41:44,286
By the desire to help
a stricken friend...

750
00:41:47,234 --> 00:41:51,141
By the need to protect
a long-buried secret.

751
00:41:54,414 --> 00:41:58,994
By the movement
of two lives in opposite directions.

752
00:42:02,002 --> 00:42:06,868
And sometimes just as one
test of loyalty ends...

753
00:42:07,944 --> 00:42:09,635
